desc: Sneakers, shoes and footworks made, created and designed for Bboying, Breakin', Break Dancing, active urban wear and the true Hip Hop culture. The first ever sneaker company of the Breakin' subculture of the Hip Hop Street Culture which represents the rise to the overground while preserving that underground essence.
